reviews.title: Been counting down the days!
reviews.comment: Awesome app! So much more convenient than having to go online every time I wanted to check my bank account.
reviews.author: Kayleigh Burzynski

reviews.title: It\'s about time.
reviews.comment: It\'s about time that CFCU got their own banking app.  There is a lot of stuff you can still only do on the web, but for checking your balance on the go, its great.
reviews.author: richard watkins

reviews.title: Does what it needs to but horrible design
reviews.comment: This app is excellent at getting the pertinent information in front of you but the design is terrible in particular because Android app design guidelines are readily available there should be no excuse in making an app look like this. Definitely needs to be redone in that sense.
reviews.author: Velija Cohodar

reviews.title: Note to developers
reviews.comment: The app desperately needs a paste option for those if us who use Last Pass and the like. And to just be able to copy paste bill pay charges from our email address. Otherwise works great!
reviews.author: Seth Dugenske

reviews.title: Finally
reviews.comment: I\'m glad we finally have this. It will come in handy for sure.
reviews.author: Matthew Campbell

reviews.title: Nice app, but please keep working on it!
reviews.comment: Nice addition to my regular online banking. App works well and gets the job done! Please keep improving it. I had some graphic glitches. It\'s also very slow to process when logging in and out.
reviews.author: Marshall Hooyman

reviews.title: Awesome!
reviews.comment: Works awesome! It is going to be so nice to have access to all my account features from my phone!
reviews.author: Dallas Janssen

reviews.title: Good, not great
reviews.comment: Was happy to finally get a banking app. That said this app is very slow and not optimized for Android. I also wish it had the check to picture deposit function like most banks are going to lately.
reviews.author: Andrew Foss

reviews.comment: Great job. Maybe a pin to log in as well as check hold info for accounts.
reviews.author: mike vanderheiden

reviews.title: Great app. Just needs1 more feature.
reviews.comment: I gave 4 stars, and not 5 because I wish I deposit payroll checks with this app. Otherwise Awesome. Thanks.
reviews.author: Todd Van Handel

reviews.comment: Awesome. Easy. Accurate. Thank you CFCU. Bye bye Tellerphone & online. Thanks.
reviews.author: Gary Snow

reviews.title: Samsung s3
reviews.comment: I been waiting a long time for this app.  Very happy:-) seems easy to use:-)
reviews.author: Steph Thielen
